<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="text-center text-primary">Technologies used on my site</h2>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center w-100">
            <button id="card-back" class="btn btn-primary me-3 fs-4">←</button>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4 scroll-card">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h4 class="card-title text-success">Entity Framework Core</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Entity Framework Core — is an object-relational mapper (ORM) for .NET,
                            which allows developers to work with databases using .NET objects,
                            eliminating the need for most code to access data.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4 scroll-card">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h4 class="card-title text-info">SignalR</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            SignalR — is a library for ASP.NET that makes it easy to add
                            real-time web functionality such as notifications,
                            chats or real-time updates to your applications.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4 scroll-card">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h4 class="card-title text-warning">ASP.NET Core</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            ASP.NET Core — it is cross-platform, high-performance,
                            open source cloud platform for creating modern
                            Internet and cloud-connected applications.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4 scroll-card">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h4 class="card-title text-primary">JS, AJAX, jQuery</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            These technologies are used to create dynamic and interactive web pages.<br />
                            <strong>JavaScript</strong> provides the framework for executing client-side logic.<br />
                            <strong>AJAX</strong> allows you to asynchronously exchange data with the server, ensuring content updates without reloading the page.<br />
                            <strong>jQuery</strong> makes working with JavaScript and AJAX easy by providing convenient methods for manipulating the DOM, handling events, and making requests to the server.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4 scroll-card">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h4 class="card-title text-danger">Sessions</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Interactive Real-Time Sessions: Our platform offers a robust session management system that allows users to create and join interactive sessions. These sessions are designed to facilitate real-time engagement, where participants can collaborate, compete, or simply learn together. Each session is backed by our powerful backend, ensuring a seamless experience. You can track your performance, compare it with others, and even analyze session data post-completion to refine your skills.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4 scroll-card">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h4 class="card-title text-light">Other</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Enhanced Social Connectivity: Our website fosters a community atmosphere by allowing you to add friends and build your own network. You can engage in private conversations through secure, one-on-one chats, making it easy to share strategies or discuss session results. Additionally, during a session, you can communicate with all participants in real time, enhancing collaboration and making each session more interactive and enjoyable. Whether you're coordinating teamwork or engaging in friendly competition, our platform supports dynamic and meaningful social interactions.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button id="card-forward" class="btn btn-primary ms-3 fs-4">→</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts
{
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            let cards = $('.scroll-card');
            let currentIndex = 0;

            // Show the first card initially
            cards.eq(currentIndex).removeClass('d-none');

            function showCard(index) {
                cards.fadeOut(500);
                cards.eq(index).fadeIn(500);
            }

            $('#card-back').click(function () {
                currentIndex = (currentIndex - 1 + cards.length) % cards.length;
                showCard(currentIndex);
            });

            $('#card-forward').click(function () {
                currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % cards.length;
                showCard(currentIndex);
            });
            // Auto-rotate cards every 10 seconds
            setInterval(function () {
                currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % cards.length;
                showCard(currentIndex);
            }, 10000);

            showCard(currentIndex);
        });
    </script>
}